  "prompt": "If I visit your country, what is one vegetarian dish not to miss?",
  "response": "If you visit India, one vegetarian dish you absolutely must try is **Paneer Butter Masala**. This creamy and rich dish features soft paneer (Indian cottage cheese) cooked in a tomato-based gravy with aromatic spices like garam masala, turmeric, and cumin, enriched with butter and cream. It's typically served with naan or rice, making it a hearty and indulgent meal. Its perfect balance of flavors and textures makes it a favorite among locals and visitors alike! \ud83c\udf36\ufe0f\ud83e\uddc8\ud83c\udf45",
